                                         "PostMention":  ""
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "#### The Shona People\n\nThe expansion of the Bantu people created about 500 different languages (<htcite0>; <htcite1>). Among the Bantu-speaking peoples are the Shona people, who, among their many known advancements, constructed what we now know as Great Zimbabwe (<htcite2>) shown in **Figure 2**.",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "c5ab3b9d-0f70-4fa2-80b7-4fc381c47187",
                                                            "text":  "Fortes-Lima, C.A., Burgarella, C., Hammarén, R. et al",
                                                            "page":  "",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2024",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "8c10d904-305e-4a71-9ccf-28e6c83f7280",
                                                            "text":  "History Tracers Team",
                                                            "page":  "Great Zimbabwe",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2025",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
