                                         "format":  "markdown",
                                         "PostMention":  ""
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "#### How did they calculate?\n\nWe have seen so far that in East Africa, there was trade and that Chinese coins were present. Furthermore, we know that the profile of the goods changed over time, indicating adaptations by the local population to the goods and changes in their needs (<htcite0>; <htcite1>). This leads us to a reflection:",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "f7381734-81dc-4bef-8527-44317f40c4b4",
                                                            "text":  "Zhao, B.",
                                                            "page":  "",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2015",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "0c717575-d51a-464d-9be6-8ecfda771376",
                                                            "text":  "History Tracers Team",
                                                            "page":  "Great Zimbabwe",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2025",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        }
                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
                                         "imgdesc":  "",
                                         "format":  "markdown",
                                         "PostMention":  ""
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection: How ....?</b><br /><br />The goods changed in size and coins were present. On the other hand, we have no known written records from the Shona, but we know they spoke a language originating from a migration that began between approximately <htdate0> and <htdate1> (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>).<br /><br >The lack of texts from one side apparently did not prevent trade. Did the Shona really not develop writing, or do we simply not know about it?<br /><br />To make payments or even barter, it is necessary to know how to evaluate something and assign it a value. Since counting systems have existed in Africa for over 30,000 years (<htcite3>), could the Shona have used their own counting system to define values?<br /><br />Assuming they had a numerical system, could it also have included the concept of zero?</div></div></center></p>",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "baffbb52-eb8f-41ee-8842-91b89ae393bb",
                                                            "text":  "Bostoen, K.",
                                                            "page":  "pp. 228",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2018",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "c38ef469-13b7-4292-b8ab-69231fbfd1da",
                                                            "text":  "Pakendorf, B., de Filippo, C., & Bostoen, K.",
                                                            "page":  "pp. 63",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2011",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "5f55c3fc-d434-4d56-a6fc-838649b8aa97",
                                                            "text":  "Yanovich, I.",
                                                            "page":  "pp. 304",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2025",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "a4f22e25-5839-407f-a1aa-634521d52b42",
                                                            "text":  "González Redondo, Francisco A., et al.",
                                                            "page":  "pp. 180 - 181",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2010",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        }
                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
                                         "imgdesc":  "",
                                         "format":  "html",
                                         "PostMention":  ""
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "The questions raised in this reflection still require in-depth studies and more information gathering in Africa so that we can answer them clearly. For now, we cannot deny that the evidence is present, and as Dr. Wilbert Z. Sadomba mentions in his work, the Shona people mastered various types of knowledge that we now explain mathematically (<htcite0>).",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "cc162709-bdc3-469b-a208-e900f4570842",
                                                            "text":  "Sadomba, Zvakanyorwa Wilbert",
                                                            "page":  "",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2024",
